    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Region:</strong> Alsace, France</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Riesling</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">A dry benchmark that shows why Riesling can work so well with seafood, roast chicken, and sharper herb-driven meals. It is clean, stony, and disciplined.</p>
  </div>
