    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Region:</strong> Mosel, Germany</p>
    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2"><strong>Variety:</strong> Riesling</p>
    <p class="text-gray-700">A strong off-dry reference for spicy food and pork. This is the style that explains why Riesling is such a good answer when heat and sweetness hit the same plate.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-6 mb-4">
    <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-wine-700 mb-2">3. Donnhoff Oberhauser Brucke Spatlese</h3>
